.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>crontab에 로그 등록</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>crontab vi로 열기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"commandline\"><pre class=\"language-commandline\"><code class=\"language-commandline\">export VISUAL=vi</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>crontab 등록</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">   *　　　　   *　　　　    *　　　　  *　　　    *\n분(0-59)  시간(0-23)　일(1-31)　월(1-12)  요일(0-7)</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"commandline\"><pre class=\"language-commandline\"><code class=\"language-commandline\">crontab -e</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"commandline\"><pre class=\"language-commandline\"><code class=\"language-commandline\"># 매일 정각에 실행됨\n00 00 * * * /home/ubuntu/delete_log.sh</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>crontab 내용 보기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"commandline\"><pre class=\"language-commandline\"><code class=\"language-commandline\">crontab -l</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2024//posts/ubuntu-delete-log","tagSlugs":["/tag/ubuntu/","/tag/crontab/","/tag/deletelog/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2024-03-26","description":"ubuntu delete log","tags":["ubuntu","crontab","delete-log"],"title":"Ubuntu 일정한 시간마다 로그 삭제하기","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2024//posts/ubuntu-delete-log"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2764776372","401334301"]}